 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; &quot;&gt;\r\n	Delivery Time ? Time Required for Delivery&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	During the ordering procedure, we will inform you of the time required for delivery and the form of delivery available for the goods purchased. Orders for items in stock will ship within 7 business days. For items that are made-to-order, orders may take up to 2-3 weeks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	However, ASHLEY ASHOFF and Company reserves the right to divide your order into partial shipments. In this case, your charge card or credit card will only be debited for the goods shipped and for a single shipment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; &quot;&gt;\r\n	Delivery Time ? Problems of Delivery&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	Any failure to deliver or late delivery exceeding (8) business days should be reported to our customer service as soon as possible. In order for your claim to be accepted, please notify us within a maximum of thirty (30) calendar days from the date of confirmation of your order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	Please check that your shipment is correct on delivery. If there are any discrepancies in your order when the products are delivered to you, please note the nature of the potential discrepancy (e.g., open package, damaged goods, etc.) by hand, if possible, on the delivery notice, and sign.&lt;/p&gt