y you shortly when your purchase ships. If you have any questions you may contact us at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@bettyconfidential.com&quot;&gt;Customer Service&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','1'),('9','3','Payment Cancelled','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	You have cancelled your payment. Click continue below to continue shopping. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@bettyconfidential.com&quot;&gt;Customer Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','1'),('11','0','Customer Service','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Please feel free to contact us with any questions you might have. We try to respond within 24 hours and pride ourselves on providing our customers with the best possible online shopping experience. We hope that you enjoy shopping on our site and that you find our product line and services satisfactory.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','1');

